snippet.title: The Escape: Together release trailer
snippet.description:
The Escape: Together is a 2 player online CO-OP psychological horror. The paranormal creature has taken over the house. You must use everything you find to survive and make your runaway.
Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2242760/The_Escape_Together/?beta=0
